Integrated Circuits & Electronics

Reduce-reuse-recycle approaches through life- cycle management for electronics-based products

Patent portfolio reflects sustainable innovation Siemens’ sustainable innovation is reflected in the compa-

ny’s patent portfolio. Using the LexisNexis® PatentSight® patent information platform, we evaluate our sustainable innovations against the United Nations’ 17 defined Sustain- able Development Goals (SDGs) and the corresponding 169 targets. 46.8% of the active patent families in Siemens’ patent portfolio relate to at least one SDG, mainly in the categories of Good Health and Well-Being (SDG 3), Industry, Innovation, and Infrastructure (SDG 9), Affordable and Clean Energy (SDG 7), and Climate Action (SDG 13).